00:12:30,579 --> 00:12:33,209
Real-time, live, not yesterday's report.

251
00:12:33,289 --> 00:12:34,049
This is right now.

252
00:12:34,899 --> 00:12:36,229
Screening process is visible.

253
00:12:36,969 --> 00:12:41,129
Screening success rate, failure
