264
00:13:14,979 --> 00:13:19,599
Screening service latency, enrichment
service error rate, alert generation

265
00:13:19,619 --> 00:13:23,209
success rate, message queue
depths, database connection health,

266
00:13:23,839 --> 00:13:25,739
cross-system visibility, one place.

267
00:13:26,399 --> 00:13:29,259
Complaints analysts
become immediately mid.

268
00:13:29,939 --> 00:13:32,759
Instead of sending an email to
an engineer asking for a database

269
00:13:32,759 --> 00:13:34,209
query, they click a button.

270
00:13:34,909 --> 00:13:37,059
Self-service, instant answer.

271
00:13:37,609 --> 00:13:40,289
They have capabilities now
they didn't have before.

272
00:13:41,099 --> 00:13:43,119
Data access without needing SQL.

273
00:13:43,619 --> 00:13:46,719
Engineering teams reduce
investigation overhead dramatically.

274
00:13:47,389 --> 00:13:50,509
An incident happens, the
dashboard shows it immediately.

275
00:13:50,979 --> 00:13:53,479
Full context, correlated events.

276
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:57,389
No need to SSH into five different
