277
00:13:57,999 --> 00:13:59,539
Root cause analysis becomes visual.

278
00:14:00,289 --> 00:14:03,289
Mean time to resolution drops from
forty-five minutes to ten minutes.

279
00:14:04,049 --> 00:14:06,959
Operational leadership sees
one dashboard instead of ten.

280
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:09,459
One number for complaints system health.

281
00:14:10,109 --> 00:14:11,949
They see the signal above the noise

282
00:14:12,449 --> 00:14:15,869
We have gone from reactive
firefighting to proactive intelligence.

283
00:14:16,339 --> 00:14:17,949
Now let's automate the response.

284
00:14:18,619 --> 00:14:21,899
The alert engine continuously
evaluates incoming log streams.

285
00:14:22,529 --> 00:14:26,919
It's looking for several patterns:
volume spikes, screening failures

286
00:14:26,919 --> 00:14:30,939
