fifty per minute, something is wrong.

287
00:14:31,249 --> 00:14:32,259
Screening failures.

288
00:14:32,709 --> 00:14:36,389
For the past thirty minutes, eight
percent of sanction checks are

289
00:14:36,389 --> 00:14:38,094
returning errors instead of results.

290
00:14:38,094 --> 00:14:41,309
That should be zero point one
percent transaction stalls.

291
00:14:41,949 --> 00:14:44,159
Customer-initiated five
hundred transaction, but

292
00:14:44,169 --> 00:14:45,459
only four eighty completed.

293
00:14:45,919 --> 00:14:46,939
Where are the other twenty?

294
00:14:47,139 --> 00:14:48,019
