295
00:14:48,629 --> 00:14:49,919
Infrastructure outages.

296
00:14:50,699 --> 00:14:54,229
The enrichment servant has been responded
to a heartbeat in ninety seconds.

297
00:14:54,339 --> 00:14:54,959
It's down.

298
00:14:55,459 --> 00:14:56,969
The detection is statistical.

299
00:14:57,659 --> 00:15:00,619
It learns baseline behavior
