300
00:15:01,089 --> 00:15:02,459
No manual tuning required.

301
00:15:02,999 --> 00:15:05,619
The system adapts as your
traffic patterns change.

302
00:15:06,459 --> 00:15:10,569
When an anomaly is detected, the alert
engine raises an alert immediately.

303
00:15:11,069 --> 00:15:12,279
Color-coded severity.

304
